He'll need to rest for a while.

282
00:25:17,839 --> 00:25:18,400
What about the police station?

283
00:25:18,559 --> 00:25:19,880
They sent someone new to take over.

284
00:25:21,000 --> 00:25:22,319
But as long as it's not Zhou Ziheng,

285
00:25:23,000 --> 00:25:24,000
the situation with Weihao...

286
00:25:24,599 --> 00:25:25,599
we can handle it.

287
00:25:32,519 --> 00:25:34,039
Why don't you ask me what happened?

288
00:25:40,079 --> 00:25:41,640
I never ask about your business.

289
00:26:21,039 --> 00:26:22,079
Why are your hands so cold?

290
00:26:24,079 --> 00:26:24,599
It's nothing.

291
00:26:25,359 --> 00:26:26,200
I'm just a bit tired.

292
00:26:26,799 --> 00:26:28,519
Can I go backstage to touch up my makeup?

293
00:26:29,519 --> 00:26:30,640
If you need anything later,

294
00:26:30,680 --> 00:26:31,480
give me a call.

295
00:26:46,480 --> 00:26:47,839
Surprised?

296
00:26:49,599 --> 00:26:52,640
You're dressed so beautifully today.

297
00:26:52,640 --> 00:26:53,559
Madam, are you crazy?

298
00:26:55,759 --> 00:26:57,759
Why do you look like you've seen a ghost?

299
00:27:00,559 --> 00:27:02,559
You didn't expect me to get out so soon, did you?

300
00:27:06,119 --> 00:27:07,240
Was it your doing?

301
00:27:08,400 --> 00:27:10,319
I got in trouble the moment you came to the company this morning.

302
00:27:10,799 --> 00:27:12,119
Don't think I don't know.

303
00:27:12,480 --> 00:27:13,480
That Superintendent who arrested me

304
00:27:13,480 --> 00:27:15,039
is a student of your Godfather.

305
00:27:17,039 --> 00:27:18,400
I don't know anything.

306
00:27:20,039 --> 00:27:21,240
You're telling me you don't know?

307
00:27:21,680 --> 00:27:22,240
Hao Yu.

308
00:27:22,599 --> 00:27:23,519
You say you don't know?

309
00:27:26,160 --> 00:27:26,880
Fine.

310
00:27:30,079 --> 00:27:30,759
Then I...

311
00:27:31,720 --> 00:27:33,559
will cut up your face right now.

312
00:27:34,640 --> 00:27:35,400
And then,

313
00:27:36,480 --> 00:27:38,279
I'll find someone to rape you.

314
00:27:38,720 --> 00:27:39,400
Let's see if

315
00:27:39,559 --> 00:27:42,000
Ji Zhijie will still want a slut like you then.

316
00:27:51,319 --> 00:27:52,000
Go ahead.

317
00:27:52,440 --> 00:27:53,519
Let everyone see.

318
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:56,200
See how you hurt people when you're high on drugs.

319
00:27:56,839 --> 00:27:57,960
Let your Jie

320
00:27:58,440 --> 00:27:59,759
and your Uncle Kun

321
00:28:00,200 --> 00:28:00,759
see.

322
00:28:01,039 --> 00:28:02,279
Let everyone see.

323
00:28:04,079 --> 00:28:04,880
What are you afraid of?

324
00:28:06,640 --> 00:28:07,400
What am I afraid of?

325
00:28:07,759 --> 00:28:09,039
Worst case, we die together.
